        currentRestorationIntro: "Cesare Battisti & Don Bosco represents two interconnected restoration projects in one building in the historic district of Isnello. The Via Cesare Battisti residence, a four-floor property, was substantially renovated beginning in 2020 and requires only minor improvements to complete. Don Bosco is currently prepped and ready to begin its restoration. While the two spaces are physically connected within the same building, Don Bosco will be a studio with its own independent, legal access from Via Don Bosco, creating a separate creative space.",
